snippet.title: The Mystery of Woolley Mountain official trailer (HD)
snippet.description: Funded on Kickstarter with backers including legend of the genre Ron Gilbert, The Mystery of Woolley Mountain is an other worldly adventure set in a fantastical world filled with strange beasts, evil witches, confused automatons and wacky ropemen. Coming 2018.
